    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一款用手指战斗、挥洒鲜血，并努力赶上侄女生日的Roguelike卡组构筑游戏。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/1e93a596478e7bfe879754b59aabfdac.poster.avif?t=1772124401\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/1e93a596478e7bfe879754b59aabfdac.webm?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/1e93a596478e7bfe879754b59aabfdac.mp4?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一名法师。一个因魔法罪行入狱、并不那么英雄的法师，被侄女的邀请从沉睡中唤醒。逃出监牢，穿越危机四伏的敌对世界。每个回合都是符印闪耀、骨骼碎裂与绝望手势交织的狂乱，你以原始的元素之力撕裂怪物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你不是天选之人，只是想当个好叔叔。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💀 <strong>掌握战术施法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是那种“打出最大卡牌”的传统卡组构筑游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/30cd52071e38fc18465aa25b95320b1a.poster.avif?t=1772124401\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/30cd52071e38fc18465aa25b95320b1a.webm?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/30cd52071e38fc18465aa25b95320b1a.mp4?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>每个法术都由你用手指直接描绘的<strong>元素图案</strong>构成。<strong>配方可以重叠与组合</strong>，激发奖励巧思与实验精神的策略。<br><br>你将发现<strong>涌现式协同</strong>不仅存在于你<i>打出什么</i>，更在于你<i>如何施放</i>——让每个回合都成为充满风险、回报与意外惊喜的高压谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🩸 <strong>血腥，但不阴郁</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索<strong>手绘黑暗幻想世界</strong>，穿越被诅咒的废墟与闹鬼森林</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对<strong>怪诞又荒谬的怪物</strong>，感受其压迫与恐惧</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在躲避狱卒的同时，将敌人<strong>击碎成焦黑的血泊</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/e19483c54437fd452bbe47ef05847917.poster.avif?t=1772124401\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/e19483c54437fd452bbe47ef05847917.webm?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/e19483c54437fd452bbe47ef05847917.mp4?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不是在拯救世界。你只是想完好无损地赶到生日派对——或许还能顺路拿到一张卡牌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>为“灵光一现！”而设计</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8位以上可玩角色，各自以独特方式改变施法系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5种以上递增难度，满足渴望挑战的玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >约一小时一局——非常适合单次畅玩</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/96f973af6dd14e88b327bc7470e06674.poster.avif?t=1772124401\" width=780 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/96f973af6dd14e88b327bc7470e06674.webm?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3057670/extras/96f973af6dd14e88b327bc7470e06674.mp4?t=1772124401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从简单图案开始，逐渐发展为复杂的互动网络——奖励实验精神与巧思，而非死记硬背。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>由两位共同创作者分担全部职责开发</i></strong><i>，所有2D资源均由艺术家DITCH WITCH制作，并由Black Lotus Software提供创意支持。</i></p>",
